<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠٩٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3997">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ يُوسُفَ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2521">أَبِي حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2676">سَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ، </a>أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِنْ كَانَ فِي شَيْءٍ فَفِي الْفَرَسِ وَالْمَرْأَةِ وَالْمَسْكَنِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>